<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT33">
<l>aṭiccakaṭañ cāṭi yaravāṭṭi yāṉai</l>
<l>piṭittocittup pēymulaiṉañ cuṇṭu vaṭippavaḷa</l>
<l>vāyppiṉṉai tōḷikkā vallēṟ ṟeruttiṟuttu</l>
<l>kōppiṉṉu māṉāṉ kuṟippu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kicking the cart with a foot, conquering the snake,</l>
<l>catching the elephant and braking [its tusks], drinking poison from</l>
<l rend="indent">the demoness’s breasts,</l>
<l>smashing the mighty bulls’ necks for the sake of Piṉṉai with beautiful red coral lips</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] shoulders,</l>
<l>He later became king [as per His] intention.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
